  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Emotional reunion for coastguard helicopter crew and Regan Green
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    It was an emotional reunion when the helicopter crew met Regan for the first time after his rescue
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

